&lt;p&gt;微软常用运行库合集_By:Dreamcast [ &lt;a href=&#34;https://wwa.lanzout.com/b0b8rs19a#9527&#34;&gt;https://wwa.lanzout.com/b0b8rs19a#9527&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;
